summary: I'm Ingeborg Hendrikx (1996) and come from The Netherlands. Since 2007 I have been a classical ballet student at the Royal Conservatoire The Hague, the Netherlands. From 2013 I studied 2 years at the Royal Ballet School of Antwerp, Belgium. After that I did my bachelor degree at The Palucca Hochschule für Tanz Dresden, Germany. I have been a professional balletdancer with the Croatian National Ballet Theatre Split HNK, Croatia for four years. During my fulltime dance carrier I was studying Communication and Multimedia Design. I worked at Anviri Cosmetics as a Junior Productmanager Online & Social Media. I was responsable for the blogs, newsletters, content designing of the social media, developing websites, designing webshop content and projectmanagement. Now I'm working at EMG NL as Digital Content Marketeer.
